<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A lopi Ie!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuhin khawvel buoina hi tawh,
 Sim leh mal ah vak mahleng;
 Van in nuoma ka lawih tiengleh,
 Mungka kipahna kim chu.

[V2]
 Thihna luigal ka kaih tiengleh,
 Kalvari tatna thisan;
 &quot;A lopi ie Hallelujah&quot;
 Tin hailo in chawian ka.

[V3]
 2. Hehpihna tincheng chu neiin,
 Makhan Lalpa a vakvai;
 Aw ka thagau thil zel inla,
 Hukdampa chu na muh ma'n.

[V4]
 3. Jerusalem tawh suok inla,
 Aw Kidron luigal lamah;
 Hukdampa chu vahawl zelin
 Kalvari na tun masieh.

[V5]
 4. Hansie huolvel zie tang achun,
 Lau loin chieh zel inla;
 Thagau, na nawpna kim ina,
 Ka Hukdampa thisan ah.

[V6]
 5. Thagau vakvaite cheng cheng chu,
 Kalvari ah chieh khawm ui;
 &quot;Aw hehpihna a mak na e&quot;,
 Tin a pak chim ngei puou hi.</lyrics>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>42</hymn_number>
</song>